headline.main: Edwards Leads No. 16 Purdue Past Northwestern, 69-65
headline.print_headline: Edwards Leads No. 16 Purdue Past Northwestern, 69-65

lead_paragraph: With a regular-season Big Ten championship already locked up, Purdue wanted to send a few more positive notes to the NCAA Selection Committee.
